n the AM. The cleanser rinses off completely, so there\u0026#39;s no interaction risk. Always follow with SPF in your morning routine.WHEN WILL I SEE RESULTS? Most people notice reduced acne within 2\u0026ndash;4 weeks of consistent use. In our independent consumer trial, 90% of users agreed skin looked visibly clearer after just 3 days. For stubborn breakouts, continue for 6\u0026ndash;8 weeks to see full benefits on acne-prone skin."
