h salicylic acid. If you also have concerns about dullness or uneven texture, our Glycolic Acid Toner can be added to your routine on alternating evenings.IS SALICYLIC ACID OR BENZOYL PEROXIDE BETTER FOR ACNE? They target different aspects of acne. Salicylic acid unclogs pores by dissolving oil and dead skin cells - it\u0026#39;s better for blackheads, congestion, and preventing acne. Benzoyl peroxide kills acne-causing bacteria - it\u0026#39;s better for inflamed pustules and papules. Our Salicylic Acid Cleanser is the better daily-use option for prevention and overall pore health. For active spots, pair it with our Succinic Acid Treatment as a targeted spot treatment. Salicylic Acid or Benzoyl Peroxide: which is better for acne? \u0026rarr;"
